aka: Bumbershoot and the Squash Blossom Queen
this_title: All Hail the Squash Blossom Queen
trans_title: Bumbershoot and the Squash Blossom Queen
introduction: A humorous coming of age drama about a wallflower, Bumbershoot, who enters a small-town beauty pageant in an effort to be noticed, not just by the beautiful girl he is smitten with, but by the community who has grossly overlooked him.
chinese_title: All Hail the Squash Blossom Queen
